UpdateDatasetReq, DeleteReq, DeleteDatasetReq, etc..

@xingxing21 
Could you please take a look at these comments:

There are now multiple URL/SSRF validators in the codebase (e.g. api/utils/web_utils.py:is_valid_url and common/data_source/rss_connector.py:_validate_url_no_ssrf) with different rules. To avoid security-policy drift, consider moving this SSRF guard into a shared utility (or strengthening/reusing the existing one) and calling it from here, so future fixes apply consistently across endpoints.
